Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:41.32,Normal,,0,0,0,,A well-know country and one of the leading economic powers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.32,0:01:45.20,Normal,,0,0,0,,But which scary story hides within it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:49.10,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,A scary story from Hong Kong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:49.10,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yes, whenever you're ready
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:59.50,Normal,,0,0,0,,This is a real story happened in a region of Hong Kong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:06.58,Normal,,0,0,0,,One night, there was a phone call in a\Ntearoom which was about to close
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:12.70,Normal,,0,0,0,,It went "ring ring ring",\Nand as the store manager answered
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:22.18,Normal,,0,0,0,,"I'd like to have... coffee... and sandwich... 3 of each, please"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:33.77,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(741,556)}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:35.22,Normal,,0,0,0,,The manager thought
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:41.24,Normal,,0,0,0,,"Who the hell makes calls this late?"\Nand set out to make the delivery
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:45.25,Normal,,0,0,0,,When he got to the house, he angrily knocked the door
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:04:55.18,Other1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,0)\pos(271.5,942)}Tearoom catering
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:50.26,Normal,,0,0,0,,And then, the door opened a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:52.36,Normal,,0,0,0,,And a voice from inside
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:55.14,Normal,,0,0,0,,Told him "place them inside"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:58.84,Normal,,0,0,0,,It was a ghastly voice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:02.00,Normal,,0,0,0,,He then put the food through the small gap on the door
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:06.36,Normal,,0,0,0,,And after he did it, the door slammed shut by itself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:13.62,Normal,,0,0,0,,He then realized the customer didn't actually\Npay him and started to shout "pay me up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:17.34,Normal,,0,0,0,,And then, money came out from under the door
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:23.02,Normal,,0,0,0,,He got so scared he immediately rode his bicycle back home
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:28.18,Normal,,0,0,0,,The next night, at the same exact time, he got the same call
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:31.26,Normal,,0,0,0,,Asking for 3 coffees and 3 sandwiches
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:34.24,Normal,,0,0,0,,Just like the day before
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:39.86,Normal,,0,0,0,,He slid the food down the door and got\Nhis money without showing his face
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:44.01,Normal,,0,0,0,,He thought "could this guy be involved in some crime?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:47.70,Normal,,0,0,0,,So he decided to bring the police with him
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:53.40,Normal,,0,0,0,,The police came and the officer said\N"it's strange, this should be a vacant house"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:55.18,Normal,,0,0,0,,"No way!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:56.70,Normal,,0,0,0,,"It can't be true"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:59.82,Normal,,0,0,0,,Then the two of them entered the room
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.76,Normal,,0,0,0,,And when they did, what they found...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:09.02,Normal,,0,0,0,,Were the rotting corpses of three men
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:13.90,Normal,,0,0,0,,The policeman stated they must have been dead for at least 2-3 months
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:19.28,Normal,,0,0,0,,"It can't be" - said the shop owner, "I got some\Ndeliveries from here the past few days"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:20.72,Normal,,0,0,0,,But no one believed him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:24.32,Normal,,0,0,0,,Some days later, the police called him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:26.54,Normal,,0,0,0,,"We performed the autopsy..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:32.30,Normal,,0,0,0,,"And we've found something like a sandwich in the corpses' stomach"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:33.30,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Ohh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:38.20,Normal,,0,0,0,,The shop owner thought again about the money he received
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:42.74,Normal,,0,0,0,,And when he looked at it, he realized it had turned into
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:46.52,Normal,,0,0,0,,Few gold-colored coins, which in Hong Kong
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:49.76,Normal,,0,0,0,,Are buried together with dead people for their afterlife
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:53.78,Normal,,0,0,0,,The money he got that day turned into these
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:55.18,Normal,,0,0,0,,And that's it
