Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.36,Normal,,0,0,0,,"But what should I do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:47.14,Normal,,0,0,0,,And so it was decided
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:52.48,Normal,,0,0,0,,That each year, 7 young male virgins
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:57.42,Normal,,0,0,0,,Would be offered to her as sacrifices to ease her anger
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:58.67,Normal,,0,0,0,,Anyway
