Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:18:05.77,Other1,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H2D2D2D&\fade(250,0)\fs46\pos(706.5,945.333)}They chose a foreigner living in Japan whose scary story\N\N\Nbest represents the country from where they come from
