Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:18:03.86,Hamada,,0,0,0,,And chose the one whose story best represents their home country
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:05.77,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Ah, so it's not a famous person?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:05.77,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:11.76,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Please
