Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:15.41,Other2,,0,0,0,,{\c&HBABAB8&\bord3\shad0\3c&H000000&\fade(250,0)\pos(726,784)}Bangladesh Representative
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:18.15,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to have you here
