Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:28.12,Other1,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H010053&\fade(250,0)\pos(807,910)}Bangladesh
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:27.56,Normal,,0,0,0,,Which scary story is born in this land?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:28.12,Other3,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\move(1000.5,590,862.5,590,16,9785)}Which scary story...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:31.09,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You can start telling your scary story
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:35.46,Normal,,0,0,0,,This is a very famous story in Bangladesh
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:39.20,Normal,,0,0,0,,I first heard it when I got back to my country during Summer break
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:42.57,Normal,,0,0,0,,And since then I still think it's really scary
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:47.51,Normal,,0,0,0,,In Bangladesh we have two types of ghosts: male and female
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:49.90,Normal,,0,0,0,,Male ghosts are called "Jin"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:52.72,Normal,,0,0,0,,And female ghosts are called "Pori"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:57.26,Normal,,0,0,0,,And because such ghosts are known as "Pori"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:19:01.39,Normal,,0,0,0,,They appear as beautiful girls
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:04.74,Normal,,0,0,0,,And they are always trying to lure men
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:06.92,Normal,,0,0,0,,So she went where this guy was
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:11.70,Normal,,0,0,0,,And she was beautiful and then she got closer and closer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:13.56,Normal,,0,0,0,,And then he ran out
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:18.38,Normal,,0,0,0,,And she run and run and run after him into a paddy field
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:23.28,Normal,,0,0,0,,And then smack, smack and she got him from his neck down
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:24.32,Normal,,0,0,0,,And then
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:30.29,Normal,,0,0,0,,His friends are like "huh? He was sleeping, wasn't he? We gotta get him away", you know, from the ghost
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:34.72,Normal,,0,0,0,,They all went together all of them, they were all afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:37.04,Normal,,0,0,0,,They all went out to search for him
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:42.32,Normal,,0,0,0,,"Oh! He's there and look!\NHis body disappeared there's only his head!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:46.18,Normal,,0,0,0,,He's--- he's been pushed till there and look,\Nthat's all you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:48.14,Normal,,0,0,0,,So they all went there
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:50.22,Normal,,0,0,0,,And ouuuuughhhh
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:52.82,Normal,,0,0,0,,They all lifted him up together
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:57.68,Normal,,0,0,0,,Some of those who lifted him then died
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:20:01.00,Normal,,0,0,0,,On the same day this story was already well known
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:04.50,Normal,,0,0,0,,And the same people, pretty much the same, the same guys
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:06.18,Normal,,0,0,0,,Were followed by the ghost
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:10.96,Normal,,0,0,0,,She was still a beautiful pretty lady and during their sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:15.98,Normal,,0,0,0,,Those guys were forced to do different stuff,\Nso no one would know
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:20.34,Normal,,0,0,0,,In Bangladesh we have huge trees,\Nlike 5 to 6 meters tall
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:24.38,Normal,,0,0,0,,And their branches, they're like extra big
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:25.60,Normal,,0,0,0,,They're big trees
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:33.54,Normal,,0,0,0,,They say if you get tangled in all those small and big\Nbranches you can't get out from them by yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:38.62,Normal,,0,0,0,,They were looking around there and they're like "hey where is he? Is he in the fields?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:40.82,Normal,,0,0,0,,"Look up that tree, look at it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.98,Normal,,0,0,0,,They were like "Aaaah we're all gonna die"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:46.13,Normal,,0,0,0,,"All our parents, all our kids, are gonna die! Quick!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.13,0:20:50.26,Normal,,0,0,0,,And lots of people here and there in the village,\Nthey died, they were dying
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:53.77,Normal,,0,0,0,,It was Summer break and I really\Nwanted to spend time outside
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:57.64,Normal,,0,0,0,,But I didn't want to be alone outside
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:21:00.64,Normal,,0,0,0,,If I only happened to see a shadow on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:04.22,Normal,,0,0,0,,Like, if I walk I'd be like "woah, am I gonna get attacked?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:08.82,Normal,,0,0,0,,Like, I felt it in my heart and even if my feet would feel itchy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:12.48,Normal,,0,0,0,,I felt like someone has always been\Nstare-stare-stare-starin' at me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:15.76,Normal,,0,0,0,,I was so scared, that town--- mama told me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:20.56,Normal,,0,0,0,,"Get back home as soon as possible, get safe inside"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.56,0:21:21.36,Normal,,0,0,0,,The end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:23.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the--!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:27.04,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,934)}The hell was that story about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:29.02,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,"The end" was so sudden
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:30.06,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Really unexpected
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.02,0:21:32.27,Normal,,0,0,0,,Lots of people saw that too
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:32.27,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm speechless
