Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.46,0:21:35.44,Normal,,0,0,0,,If you ask some
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:38.25,Normal,,0,0,0,,They would reply that they did see it for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:40.94,Normal,,0,0,0,,You know? On the countryside we have these trees
